        "content": "üìä Google Sheets Configuration\n\n**Sheet 1: \"Websites\"**\nRequired Headers:\n- url - Website URLs to monitor\n\n**Sheet 2: \"Monitoring Log\"**\nAuto-populated Headers:\n- timestamp - Analysis timestamp\n- url - Website analyzed\n- severity - critical/warning/info\n- performanceScore - Performance rating (0-100)\n- responseTime - Response time in ms\n- sslStatus - SSL certificate status\n- securityScore - Security rating (0-100)\n- issues - Detected problems\n- recommendations - Improvement suggestions\n\nüîó Service Account Permissions:\nGrant \"Editor\" access to your Google Sheets service account"
