      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 496,
        "height": 592,
        "content": "üõ†Ô∏è AI-Powered Website Monitoring System\n\nThis workflow monitors multiple websites using AI analysis and MCP tools for comprehensive performance and security monitoring.\n\n‚úÖ **Step 1: Install Required MCP Servers**\n- Install browser-tools-mcp for performance analysis\n- Install mcp-recon for security and SSL monitoring\n- Configure server endpoints in environment variables\n\n‚úÖ **Step 2: Setup Google Sheets Integration**\n- Create \"Websites\" sheet with URL column\n- Create \"Monitoring Log\" sheet for results tracking\n- Set GOOGLE_SHEET_ID environment variable\n\n‚úÖ **Step 3: Configure Notifications**\n- Set up Slack webhook/bot for alerts\n- Configure SMTP settings for email notifications\n- Set SLACK_CHANNEL, ALERT_EMAIL, FROM_EMAIL variables\n\n‚úÖ **Step 4: Customize Monitoring Settings**\n- Update monitoring thresholds in Configuration Variables\n- Add your websites to monitor\n- Adjust batch processing and alert severity rules\n\nüß™ **Final Step: Test Complete System**\nTrigger manually to verify MCP servers, analysis, and notifications work properly"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
